Emperor Magus Caligula (born Magnus "Masse" Broberg, 23 May 1973) is a Swedish extreme metal musician best known as the former vocalist, bassist and lyricist of Swedish black metal band Dark Funeral, performing for the band between 1995 and 2010.
In July 2011, Witchery announced Caligula was joining the band, replacing Legion until 2016.
